oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Unidentified Recording of Hank Snow #1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features twelve songs recorded by Hank Snow. The song "Willie Thomas" features an unknown female voice. The tape is undated. This tape is thirty-six of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow;
